WEBVTT

00:00:27.760 --> 00:00:28.920
Threat.

00:00:46.120 --> 00:00:47.050
Investigation.

00:00:47.640 --> 00:00:48.360
Three days.

00:00:57.240 --> 00:00:58.240
Three days?

00:01:00.080 --> 00:01:01.880
I'm afraid that's not possible.

00:01:02.040 --> 00:01:03.320
That's your problem.

00:01:04.160 --> 00:01:05.239
If you can't do it,

00:01:06.200 --> 00:01:08.400
you know what the consequences will be.

00:01:19.360 --> 00:01:20.520
In these noble houses,

00:01:20.520 --> 00:01:22.280
people's intentions are unpredictable.

00:01:22.280 --> 00:01:23.560
Everyone here is shrewd,

00:01:23.560 --> 00:01:25.820
not a single person you'd want to offend.

00:01:26.120 --> 00:01:26.960
But now I've

00:01:27.080 --> 00:01:28.410
already offended them.

00:01:29.440 --> 00:01:31.170
I advise you to know your place.

00:01:31.600 --> 00:01:34.860
You don't want to make enemies as soon as you arrive, do you?

00:01:35.240 --> 00:01:36.560
If you try to be meek and humble,

00:01:36.560 --> 00:01:38.759
you'll still make just as many enemies.

00:01:38.840 --> 00:01:40.039
No matter how large their army is,

00:01:40.039 --> 00:01:41.479
I have my own way to defeat them.

00:01:41.479 --> 00:01:42.340
Then do you know

00:01:42.640 --> 00:01:44.240
within these towering walls

00:01:44.479 --> 00:01:46.410
you'll eventually become a ghost?

00:01:46.520 --> 00:01:47.479
Then so be it.

00:01:50.280 --> 00:01:51.120
I've noticed that you

00:01:51.120 --> 00:01:52.759
really love to meddle in others' business.

00:01:52.759 --> 00:01:54.440
I'll enter my mansion, you do your job.

00:01:54.440 --> 00:01:55.840
Let's keep to ourselves

00:01:55.960 --> 00:01:58.220
and not interfere with each other, okay?

00:01:59.800 --> 00:02:00.840
Get out!

00:02:06.160 --> 00:02:06.720
Nongyu.

00:02:07.080 --> 00:02:08.000
I don't understand.

00:02:08.000 --> 00:02:10.320
You've gone to such lengths to trap yourself here.

00:02:10.320 --> 00:02:11.560
Surrounded by enemies.

00:02:11.560 --> 00:02:12.720
Every step is a struggle.

00:02:12.720 --> 00:02:14.450
Is this really what you wanted?

00:02:38.960 --> 00:02:42.120
Child, your life has finally been saved.

00:02:42.520 --> 00:02:44.780
You've been through death once already.

00:02:49.800 --> 00:02:50.680
Who are you?

00:02:51.920 --> 00:02:53.680
You can call me Yanbo.

00:02:55.520 --> 00:02:56.520
What's your name?

00:03:01.560 --> 00:03:03.760
If you don't want to answer, I won't ask.

00:03:04.160 --> 00:03:05.640
Born in chaotic times.

00:03:06.200 --> 00:03:10.400
Perhaps it's better to be nameless.

00:03:14.000 --> 00:03:15.280
Come, child.

00:03:15.720 --> 00:03:17.250
Drink this medicine first.

00:03:27.640 --> 00:03:29.720
At least she understands the rules.

00:03:30.280 --> 00:03:31.720
She listens when I speak.

00:03:32.360 --> 00:03:34.440
But who can't act submissive?

00:03:35.400 --> 00:03:36.680
She said herself

00:03:37.160 --> 00:03:39.160
that she'll stay in that courtyard.

00:03:39.640 --> 00:03:40.760
For all matters,

00:03:40.760 --> 00:03:43.090
she needs my approval as her elder sister.

00:03:44.200 --> 00:03:45.530
She's obedient for now.

00:03:46.000 --> 00:03:47.360
But as time goes by,

00:03:48.120 --> 00:03:49.720
who knows what might happen?

00:03:52.160 --> 00:03:53.360
You've done well.

00:03:56.160 --> 00:03:57.200
Father.

00:03:58.480 --> 00:04:01.760
Shiyuan is completely devoted to you.

00:04:10.720 --> 00:04:12.920
Thank you for your generosity, Father.

00:04:17.240 --> 00:04:19.040
Come.

00:04:21.000 --> 00:04:21.800
Father,

00:04:22.200 --> 00:04:25.400
what will you paint after finishing this one?

00:04:29.440 --> 00:04:31.880
Look at you, Father, so forgetful.

00:04:32.120 --> 00:04:34.000
Don't you always paint

00:04:34.600 --> 00:04:36.400
the new girls when they arrive?

00:04:38.000 --> 00:04:40.000
I really did forget about that.

00:04:41.280 --> 00:04:42.740
We can't break tradition.

00:04:43.600 --> 00:04:44.730
Let's do it tonight.

00:04:45.560 --> 00:04:47.020
Go make the arrangements.

00:04:49.200 --> 00:04:49.680
Yes.

00:04:51.400 --> 00:04:53.240
Please get changed quickly, beautiful lady,

00:04:53.240 --> 00:04:55.040
don't keep Master Chen waiting.

00:04:55.480 --> 00:04:56.610
What does this mean?

00:04:56.800 --> 00:04:58.320
According to the mansion's rules,

00:04:58.320 --> 00:04:59.840
Master Chen must paint

00:04:59.840 --> 00:05:01.900
a bathing portrait of every new girl.

00:05:02.080 --> 00:05:03.210
A bathing portrait?

00:05:07.000 --> 00:05:08.480
Would you both please leave first?

00:05:08.480 --> 00:05:09.740
I can manage by myself.

00:05:13.640 --> 00:05:14.600
I'll be quick.

00:05:26.400 --> 00:05:27.560
That old eunuch.

00:05:28.600 --> 00:05:29.960
Loose lips sink ships.

00:05:33.040 --> 00:05:34.560
Officer Li, your habit of showing up uninvited

00:05:34.560 --> 00:05:35.490
needs to change.

00:05:36.000 --> 00:05:37.720
I was just patrolling nearby.

00:05:38.720 --> 00:05:41.440
This courtyard is under my supervision.

00:05:42.080 --> 00:05:42.940
Let me tell you,

00:05:43.120 --> 00:05:44.720
though Chen Jingbian is a eunuch,

00:05:44.720 --> 00:05:45.980
he still abuses women.

00:05:47.560 --> 00:05:49.200
Even if I'm a lamb in the tiger's mouth,

00:05:49.200 --> 00:05:50.930
what can Officer Li do about it?

00:05:51.800 --> 00:05:53.659
If you promise to leave this place

00:05:53.880 --> 00:05:54.880
and never return,

00:05:55.200 --> 00:05:56.800
I promise to help you escape.

00:05:58.080 --> 00:05:59.640
Then I'd rather not have your help.

00:05:59.640 --> 00:06:01.520
You've already saved me anyway,

00:06:01.760 --> 00:06:02.620
more than once.

00:06:02.760 --> 00:06:04.320
You don't understand Chen Jingbian.

00:06:04.320 --> 00:06:05.520
You won't be able to endure it.

00:06:05.520 --> 00:06:07.520
It's you who doesn't understand me.

00:06:08.480 --> 00:06:09.800
What I've been through,

00:06:09.800 --> 00:06:11.130
you know nothing about.

00:06:12.920 --> 00:06:14.850
Please leave now, I need to change.

00:06:21.520 --> 00:06:24.000
Please, Master Chen, avenge my family.

00:06:29.400 --> 00:06:30.200
Let me ask you,

00:06:31.240 --> 00:06:34.370
if I hadn't knocked that knife out of your hand back then,

00:06:34.720 --> 00:06:35.580
would you have?

00:06:37.000 --> 00:06:37.560
I would.

00:06:51.880 --> 00:06:52.360
My legs!

00:06:53.120 --> 00:06:55.159
My legs!

00:06:56.360 --> 00:06:56.840
Child.

00:06:57.320 --> 00:06:57.640
Child.

00:06:57.640 --> 00:06:58.040
Yanbo.

00:06:58.040 --> 00:06:58.700
Don't move.

00:06:58.800 --> 00:07:00.320
Yanbo, this isn't me.

00:07:00.880 --> 00:07:01.640
This isn't me.

00:07:01.640 --> 00:07:02.720
I'm not like this.

00:07:03.080 --> 00:07:05.010
I don't want to be like this, Yanbo.

00:07:05.200 --> 00:07:05.640
Child.

00:07:05.960 --> 00:07:07.840
Your injuries are too severe.

00:07:08.360 --> 00:07:10.880
It's already fortunate that you survived.

00:07:10.880 --> 00:07:12.140
Yanbo, please save me.

00:07:12.200 --> 00:07:13.600
I don't want to be like this.

00:07:13.600 --> 00:07:14.800
I must stand up again.

00:07:14.800 --> 00:07:15.920
